title: Status report: Here’s a midyear check of projects
text:
Apartment Sales Tracker Home / News / Construction & Development / Status report: Here’s a midyear check of projects Work on the Minnesota Senate Building in St. Paul is 60 percent complete. The building -- in the shadow of the State Capitol -- will offer Senate hearing rooms and offices for senators and staff. (Staff photos: Bill Klotz) Status report: Here’s a midyear check of projects By: Casey Selix July 3, 2015 7:06 am 0 
Developers and contractors continue to be the busiest we’ve seen since the recession started in 2007. Today Finance & Commerce reporters and photographer Bill Klotz check on several projects, starting with the Minnesota Senate Building in St. Paul. More projects will be featured in Tuesday’s publication. 
–Casey Selix, Editor
